Changes in build7

1. Added fault handler entry in file "kernel/fault.asm".

2. Added and set fault handler in file "kernel/traps.c"

3. Fixed the issue that function `__itoa(const char* buffer, u64 number, int base, u8 precision, u8 flags)` in file "kernel/printk.c" cannot handle 64-bit data correctly.

4. Moved screen initialization code to function `void init_screen()` in file "kernel/printk.c"